# [Welcome to Upscayl 👋](https://upscayl.org)

### 🍿 Upscayl is a free and open source desktop application that lets you upscale your low resolution images using advanced AI Models.

#### 🤓 What can Upscayl do?

- Work on Linux🐧, MacOS 🍏 and Windows 🐌
- Upscale Images 🖼
- Make your images go from 🤮 to 🤩
- Batch Upscale Images 👯
- Sharpen your Images 🔪
- Make your Gigapixel friends jealous 😡

#### 😅 What can Upscayl not do?

- Your laundry 🤓
